{
  "id": "63dda05d13d4bb001e8f511b",
  "title": "日本の暦",
  "created": 1675468895,
  "updated": 1675472031,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63dda05d13d4bb001e8f511b",
      "text": "日本の暦",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675468895,
      "updated": 1675468895
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda05f5e90c00000564c49",
      "text": "ニッポニカと[暦wiki https://eco.mtk.nao.ac.jp/koyomi/wiki/]の記述を元にざくざく",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675468895,
      "updated": 1675471871
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda0a65e90c00000564c4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675468966,
      "updated": 1675468966
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda9e15e90c00000564c54",
      "text": "暦の始まり",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471329,
      "updated": 1675471334
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda1205e90c00000564c50",
      "text": " [欽明天皇]14年 (553) 6月に、[百済]から[暦博士]が来朝した",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469088,
      "updated": 1675472031
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda0615e90c00000564c4b",
      "text": "  [日本書紀]に記載。書類上に残る最初の記録",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675468897,
      "updated": 1675471371
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa0b5e90c00000564c5c",
      "text": "   これ以前はどういう暦だったか不明",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471371,
      "updated": 1675471384
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda0da5e90c00000564c4d",
      "text": "  暦博士の名前は「固徳王保孫」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469018,
      "updated": 1675469102
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda0605e90c00000564c4a",
      "text": " 正史において初めて暦が採用されたのは[持統天皇]4年 (690) 11月",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675468896,
      "updated": 1675469232
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda1485e90c00000564c51",
      "text": "  [元嘉]・[儀鳳]という[中国暦]が行われたらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469128,
      "updated": 1675469167
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda9e95e90c00000564c56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471337,
      "updated": 1675471337
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa195e90c00000564c5d",
      "text": "大衍暦 (763~859)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471385,
      "updated": 1675471417
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda1745e90c00000564c52",
      "text": " [天平宝字]7年 (763) 8月より[大衍暦]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469172,
      "updated": 1675469226
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda1975e90c00000564c53",
      "text": "  [続日本紀]に記載。以後およそ100年にわたって使用",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469207,
      "updated": 1675469369
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda1f25e90c0000093a5ad",
      "text": "  途中[遣唐使]が[五紀暦]を持ち帰るも習学者なし",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469298,
      "updated": 1675469345
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa3c5e90c00000564c5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471421,
      "updated": 1675471421
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa3d5e90c00000564c5f",
      "text": "宣明暦 (859~1684)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471421,
      "updated": 1675471436
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda2215e90c0000093a5ae",
      "text": " [貞観]1年 (859) に[長慶宣明暦経]が[渤海]から渡来",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469345,
      "updated": 1675469468
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda2b45e90c0000093a5b1",
      "text": "  いわゆる[宣明暦]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469492,
      "updated": 1675469496
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda2815e90c0000093a5af",
      "text": "  貞観3年に大春日朝臣真野麻呂の申請により正式採用",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469441,
      "updated": 1675469500
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda0f75e90c00000564c4e",
      "text": "  以後823年使用され続ける",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469047,
      "updated": 1675469518
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda37b5e90c0000093a5bd",
      "text": "   暦法の計算上、後代になればなるほどズレが広がってきてしまった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469691,
      "updated": 1675469730
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda3d55e90c0000093a5bf",
      "text": "    >太陽年は (365.24464 - 365.2422) × 800 ≒ 2、すなわち800年使い続けると2日ほどのずれとなります。渋川春海が「宣明暦、天に後る二日なる」と述べているのはこの点です。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469781,
      "updated": 1675469790
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda3e15e90c0000093a5c1",
      "text": "    [https://eco.mtk.nao.ac.jp/koyomi/wiki/C0EBCCC0CEF1.html 暦Wiki/宣明暦]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469793,
      "updated": 1675469820
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda35d5e90c0000093a5bc",
      "text": "    江戸時代になると誤差が2日ほど出ている",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469661,
      "updated": 1675469755
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddab225e90c00000564c67",
      "text": "  なので平安～江戸初期までの暦を知りたい場面では宣明暦を参照すればいいってことだな[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon*3]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471651,
      "updated": 1675471692
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa535e90c00000564c60",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471443,
      "updated": 1675471443
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa535e90c00000564c61",
      "text": "貞享暦 (1684~1754)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471443,
      "updated": 1675471480
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda2cf5e90c0000093a5b3",
      "text": " 貞享1年 (1684) [渋川春海]の作成した[貞享暦]が採用される",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469518,
      "updated": 1675469627
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda3325e90c0000093a5b7",
      "text": "  三度の改暦の上奏を経ている",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469618,
      "updated": 1675469630
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda33f5e90c0000093a5ba",
      "text": "   この辺は[天地明察]が詳しい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469631,
      "updated": 1675469650
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda3515e90c0000093a5bb",
      "text": "    (らしい[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469650,
      "updated": 1675471588
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda4035e90c0000093a5c2",
      "text": "  これが日本史上初の日本独自の暦",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469827,
      "updated": 1675469859
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa7c5e90c00000564c62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471484,
      "updated": 1675471484
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaa7c5e90c00000564c63",
      "text": "[宝暦暦] (1755~1797)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471484,
      "updated": 1675471555
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda4c15e90c0000093a5c9",
      "text": " その後細かい修正が行われる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470018,
      "updated": 1675470025
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda4cc5e90c0000093a5ca",
      "text": "  天文学に興味のあった[徳川吉宗]は西洋天文学を導入した改暦を意図した",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470027,
      "updated": 1675470192
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaad65e90c00000564c65",
      "text": "   この辺は[江戸壊滅の危機！すい星激突の恐怖]が詳しい(?)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471574,
      "updated": 1675471630
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddab075e90c00000564c66",
      "text": "    ご覧になった方ご意見求む[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471623,
      "updated": 1675471640
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda5155e90c0000093a5cb",
      "text": "   [西川如見]の子、[正休]を[天文方]に据える",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470101,
      "updated": 1675470876
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda5be5e90c0000093a5cd",
      "text": "    春海の子[渋川則休]とともに、[陰陽頭][土御門泰邦]と改暦の相談を進めた ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470271,
      "updated": 1675470885
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda5d25e90c0000093a5ce",
      "text": "  しかし下記の事情や土御門泰邦との不和が重なり、正休は退けられることに",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470290,
      "updated": 1675470890
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda6955e90c0000093a5d2",
      "text": "   [寛延]3年(1750)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470485,
      "updated": 1675470485
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda6835e90c0000093a5cf",
      "text": "    [桜町天皇]の崩御",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470467,
      "updated": 1675470487
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda6df5e90c0000093a5d5",
      "text": "    渋川則休の急死",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470559,
      "updated": 1675470579
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda69a5e90c0000093a5d4",
      "text": "   同4年 (1751)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470490,
      "updated": 1675470505
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda6885e90c0000093a5d0",
      "text": "    吉宗の死去",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470472,
      "updated": 1675470499
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda44f5e90c0000093a5c4",
      "text": "  宝暦5年 (1755) に土御門泰邦により[宝暦甲戌元暦] ([宝暦暦]) が施行されるも、宝暦13年 (1763) に日食が暦に記載されなかったという大ミスが発覚",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469903,
      "updated": 1675471566
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda7815e90c0000093a5d8",
      "text": "   貞享暦をわずかに補正したものの、理論的には変化がない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470721,
      "updated": 1675470924
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda8955e90c0000093a5dd",
      "text": "   このミスを受けて、明和元年 (1764) には[山路主住]、[佐々木文次郎] ([吉田秀長]) を天文方に任じさらなる改暦へ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470997,
      "updated": 1675471120
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda8ef5e90c0000093a5de",
      "text": "  明和8年 (1771) より[修正宝暦甲戌元暦]施行",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471087,
      "updated": 1675471147
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda7b35e90c0000093a5d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675470771,
      "updated": 1675470807
    },
    {
      "id": "63ddaab75e90c00000564c64",
      "text": "[寛政暦]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675471543,
      "updated": 1675471548
    },
    {
      "id": "63dda4145e90c0000093a5c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1675469844,
      "updated": 1675469844
    }
  ]
}